No!

1305
01:34:01.240 --> 01:34:04.400
I have no idea
what the fuck is going on here.

1306
01:34:07.320 --> 01:34:08.640
But this ends now.

1307
01:34:13.920 --> 01:34:15.360
Damn right it does.

1308
01:34:24.560 --> 01:34:26.240
Trudy. be careful.

1309
01:34:29.960 --> 01:34:31.000
Santa!

1310
01:34:32.040 --> 01:34:33.760
Oh. no. Santa.

1311
01:34:35.560 --> 01:34:36.560
Oh. no.

1312
01:34:44.120 --> 01:34:45.280
You saved my daughter.

1313
01:34:46.440 --> 01:34:47.520
No.

1314
01:34:48.720 --> 01:34:50.000
She saved me.

1315
01:34:50.640 --> 01:34:52.960
Help him. Please help him.

1316
01:34:53.040 --> 01:34:55.040
Honey. I don't think
there's anything we can do.

1317
01:34:55.320 --> 01:34:56.400
It's okay...

1318
01:34:56.960 --> 01:34:58.200
It's too late for that.

1319
01:34:58.640 --> 01:34:59.680
Too late.

1320
01:35:01.440 --> 01:35:02.480
I'm cold.

1321
01:35:04.560 --> 01:35:06.040
I haven't felt cold in years.

1322
01:35:06.920 --> 01:35:08.200
We need to keep him warm.

1323
01:35:09.600 --> 01:35:11.080
All of the fires are going out.

1324
01:35:11.160 --> 01:35:12.920
We need to find something to burn.

1325
01:35:15.400 --> 01:35:16.400
I got an idea.

1326
01:35:23.080 --> 01:35:24.080
No.

1327
01:35:24.160 --> 01:35:25.960
No... no. No. Jason. no.

1328
01:35:26.200 --> 01:35:27.200
Please. Santa.

1329
01:35:27.560 --> 01:35:29.360
I don't want you to die.

1330
01:35:33.480 --> 01:35:36.080
Jason. let's slow this down.
What are you doing?

1331
01:35:36.920 --> 01:35:39.200
I've lived longer
than any man should ever live.

1332
01:35:39.520 --> 01:35:41.800
He's pretty much dead.
What the hell is happening?

1333
01:35:41.880 --> 01:35:44.160
- You don't need to burn money.
- Okay. More. Yeah.

1334
01:35:44.280 --> 01:35:47.040
You can't die. Santa.
You have to get up.

1335
01:35:47.120 --> 01:35:49.320
I think I used up
all my Christmas magic.

1336
01:35:50.840 --> 01:35:51.920
Sorry.

1337
01:35:54.200 --> 01:35:57.400
I'm s... I'm sorry I can't
give you what you asked for.

1338
01:35:59.680 --> 01:36:00.680
Take that...

1339
01:36:00.760 --> 01:36:01.920
But you did.

1340
01:36:05.680 --> 01:36:07.520
Santa. please don't die.

1341
01:36:07.960 --> 01:36:10.200
Wake up...

1342
01:36:10.280 --> 01:36:11.800
We need to get him close to the fire.

1343
01:36:12.560 --> 01:36:13.560
Jason.

1344
01:36:15.920 --> 01:36:16.920
Just wake up.

1345
01:36:18.200 --> 01:36:19.200
Please.

1346
01:36:19.480 --> 01:36:20.520
No.

1347
01:36:25.960 --> 01:36:28.040
Oh. I am so. so sorry.

1348
01:36:33.320 --> 01:36:34.400
This man...

1349
01:36:36.760 --> 01:36:40.200
This brave. brave man.
whoever he was...

1350
01:36:40.280 --> 01:36:41.320
He's Santa.

1351
01:36:41.760 --> 01:36:43.600
The real Santa. He is.

1352
01:36:44.200 --> 01:36:46.000
And I still believe in him.

1353
01:36:47.400 --> 01:36:49.560
I'll always believe in you. Santa.

1354
01:36:54.720 --> 01:36:56.000
I believe in him. too.

1355
01:36:59.160 --> 01:37:00.520
He saved Trudy.

1356
01:37:02.000 --> 01:37:03.560
He saved our family.

1357
01:37:06.040 --> 01:37:07.400
What's realer than that?

1358
01:37:12.280 --> 01:37:13.320
Then maybe...

1359
01:37:16.440 --> 01:37:17.680
I believe in him. too.

1360
01:37:19.240 --> 01:37:20.240
So do I.

1361
01:37:21.800 --> 01:37:23.680
Oh. shit.

1362
01:37:24.480 --> 01:37:25.480
I guess...

1363
01:37:26.640 --> 01:37:28.000
I guess I do. too.

1364
01:37:28.600 --> 01:37:30.000
Fuck me.

1365
01:37:30.520 --> 01:37:31.680
I believe. too.

1366
01:37:42.560 --> 01:37:43.560
Oh. my God.

1367
01:37:43.720 --> 01:37:44.720
Santa!

1368
01:37:50.120 --> 01:37:51.120
You...

1369
01:37:52.720 --> 01:37:53.760
You were dead.

1370
01:37:55.240 --> 01:37:56.680
Christmas magic.

1371
01:37:58.160 --> 01:38:00.000
I still don't really understand...

1372
01:38:00.840 --> 01:38:01.960
how it works.

1373
01:38:08.200 --> 01:38:09.200
Thank you.

1374
01:38:10.080 --> 01:38:11.600
I don't know
how we can ever repay you.

1375
01:38:12.120 --> 01:38:13.496
Well. you brought me back
from the dead

1376
01:38:13.520 --> 01:38:14.680
so we'll call it even.

1377
01:38:16.400 --> 01:38:17.400
Even?

1378
01:38:17.480 --> 01:38:19.360
We just burned
half a million dollars.

1379
01:38:20.720 --> 01:38:21.760
Look. Santa!

1380
01:38:22.120 --> 01:38:23.160
Look who came.

1381
01:38:30.520 --> 01:38:33.480
Now you show up. huh?

1382
01:38:34.280 --> 01:38:35.360
You leave me here to die

1383
01:38:35.440 --> 01:38:37.200
come back after
all the work's done. huh?

1384
01:38:37.320 --> 01:38:40.120
You know what?
I should make you guys into a stew

1385
01:38:40.200 --> 01:38:41.520
and feed you to the elves!

1386
01:38:43.840 --> 01:38:48.200
Yes. Blitzen!
Yes. I'm talking to you!

1387
01:38:48.840 --> 01:38:50.400
You. too. Prancer.

1388
01:38:55.840 --> 01:38:57.200
You got my sack.

1389
01:38:57.920 --> 01:39:01.000
My spare... You went home
and you got my spare sack?

1390
01:39:03.600 --> 01:39:06.280
Oh. God.
I can't stay mad at you guys. I...

1391
01:39:08.680 --> 01:39:11.000
I can't...

1392
01:39:28.520 --> 01:39:29.600
Hello. beautiful.

1393
01:39:29.960 --> 01:39:31.200
Skullcrusher!

1394
01:39:44.040 --> 01:39:45.360
Guess this is goodbye.

1395
01:39:46.040 --> 01:39:47.120
I got to go.

1396
01:39:47.840 --> 01:39:49.040
Do you have to?

1397
01:39:53.360 --> 01:39:55.320
It's Christmas Eve.
and there's a lot of...

1398
01:39:55.480 --> 01:39:58.320
boys and girls on the nice list
that want their presents. you know?

1399
01:40:01.320 --> 01:40:02.360
Thank you.

1400
01:40:03.600 --> 01:40:04.640
For what?

1401
01:40:05.320 --> 01:40:06.520
For believing in me.

1402
01:40:07.360 --> 01:40:09.560
For reminding me
that Christmas still matters.

1403
01:40:11.560 --> 01:40:12.800
And that I still...

1404
01:40:14.120 --> 01:40:15.160
matter.

1405
01:40:17.840 --> 01:40:19.520
You gave me my "ho. ho. ho" back.

1406
01:40:29.360 --> 01:40:31.040
All right. Get out of here.

1407
01:40:35.040 --> 01:40:37.200
Merry Christmas!

1408
01:40:41.160 --> 01:40:44.640
Now. Dasher! Now. Dancer!

1409
01:40:44.880 --> 01:40:46.880
Now. Prancer and Vixen!

1410
01:40:46.960 --> 01:40:50.000
On. Comet! On. Cupid!

1411
01:40:50.200 --> 01:40:52.680
On. Donner and Blitzen!

1412
01:40:53.000 --> 01:40:56.200
Come on. you beautiful bastards!

1413
01:40:56.560 --> 01:40:59.400
We've got some work to do!

1414
01:41:02.560 --> 01:41:04.680
Ho. ho. ho!

1415
01:41:05.120 --> 01:41:08.080
Merry Christmas!

1416
01:42:32.960 --> 01:42:35.000
Hey. yo! What's Gucci. squad fam?

1417
01:42:35.080 --> 01:42:38.000
It's the Bert Locker.
living the dream.

1418
01:42:38.080 --> 01:42:40.360
You know what?
See this guy? Dead as hell.

1419
01:42:40.440 --> 01:42:41.840
Santa's real. all right?

1420
01:42:41.920 --> 01:42:43.240
Don't end up on the naughty list.

1421
01:42:43.520 --> 01:42:44.560
Do better.

1422
01:42:44.720 --> 01:42:45.800
Bert Lightstone out.

1422
